- (32-bit) Added `Save' button to the BASIC listing window, where BASIC listings
  can be saved out to an ASCII file;
- (32-bit) Added soundcard detection info to the `SysInfo' window;
- (32-bit) Added option `Sound volume' to the menu strip;
